description:
The Multiresolution Intrinsic Segmentation Template (MIST) brain atlas provides volumetric parcellations at 
    different spatial scales. Here are available the scales 7, 12, 20, 36, and 64.
reference:
Urchs S, Armoza J, Moreau C et al. MIST: A multi-resolution parcellation of functional brain networks. 
     MNI Open Res 2019, 1:3 (https://doi.org/10.12688/mniopenres.12767.2)
